nodes.text: Docking bay 33 was a landing bay that was located in Kwilaan Spaceport on the planet Naboo. In about 32 BBY, the terrorist group the Army of Life parked the YT-1300 light freighter Majestic Gundark in docking bay 33 and hired a group of agents to use the vessel to transport some crates of clodhoppers to the planet Stend IV. The agents traveled to the bay to take control of the YT-1300, but on arrival there, they were confronted by some security officers, who suspected that the agents were involved in smuggling.
